{"word":"ἐξεπίσταμαι","slug":"ἐξεπίσταμαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐξεπίσταμαι</b></el> <p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to know thoroughly, know well</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, attic; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <i>to know well how</i> to do, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/>"}]}